snippet.title: Bakra Nahi Majnu Halaal - Part 2 : Full On Farziwada - Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Download Skkily Ludo App From 
https://bit.ly/Amit-bhadana

REFERRAL CODE - AMIT100


Jab aag lagi hai to dhamaka to ho kar rahega. Hamare Majnu ne le lie hain bade wala panga. 2 ladkiyon ko date toh bahut log karte hain lekin hamara hero 2 sagi behnon se pyar kar baitha hani. Lalach buri bala hain Rinku na Raveena se breakup karna chahata hai aur na hi Sangeeta ko ta-ta bye-bye, aur ab vo galti se pahunch gaya hain dono ke ghar jahan bas phootne hi wala hai uska bhaanda. Kya hoga aage isi baat ka hai sabko intezaar. Kya Sangeeta aur Raveena mil kar karengi Rinku ko halal ya unke papa karenge hamare Majnu ka kaam tamaam? Kya hoga is love story ka end? Ye sab pata chalega is part mein. To sab mil kar hamare Majnu ke lie prarthna karo aur poore parivaar family ke sath dekho ye kamaal dhamaal story. Dhnyaawad :)

snippet.title: DAMaN (In Hindi) Official Trailer | Babushaan Mohanty, Dipanwit D | In Cinemas 3rd February 2023
snippet.description:
In 2015, a young doctor, Dr. Siddharth Mohanty, who has just completed his MBBS from a government medical college, is posted  to a back of beyond tribal area in the Malkangiri district. Janbai PHC has 151 villages under it, is  infamous for its Naxal dominance and doesn't even boast of the most basic facilities. 
Dr. Siddharth Mohanty arrives reluctantly, wanting to quit at the earliest. But fate wills otherwise.  Daman is the story of 151 villages and one doctor to control the spread of malaria, the tussle between superstition and medical science. 

Presenting you the official trailer of DAMaN in Hindi.

localized.title: DAMaN (In Hindi) Official Trailer | Babushaan Mohanty, Dipanwit D | In Cinemas 3rd February 2023
localized.description:
In 2015, a young doctor, Dr. Siddharth Mohanty, who has just completed his MBBS from a government medical college, is posted  to a back of beyond tribal area in the Malkangiri district. Janbai PHC has 151 villages under it, is  infamous for its Naxal dominance and doesn't even boast of the most basic facilities. 
Dr. Siddharth Mohanty arrives reluctantly, wanting to quit at the earliest. But fate wills otherwise.  Daman is the story of 151 villages and one doctor to control the spread of malaria, the tussle between superstition and medical science. 

Presenting you the official trailer of DAMaN in Hindi.

Tere Bin Episode 06 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 12th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: Sweet Pongal Recipe in Tamil | Sakkarai Pongal Recipe in Tamil | Chakkarai Pongal
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make sweet pongal recipe in tamil. Sakkarai pongal is a great recipe which brings back so many warm memories, the soft fluffy cooked rice and dal with jaggery and roasted nuts is a great way to start the morning. This is pongal recipe is very easy to make and we can make pongal either in a pot or in a pressure cooker.


Sweet Pongal in pot :- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ESuqXoJj4M0
Sweet Pongal in cooker :- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AgWLO_cV7zw

Wish you all a very happy Pongal 2023 and have fun. Also, please do make this sweet pongal and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!

Ingredients:
1 cup Raw Rice
1/2 cup Moong Dal
1 cup Milk
1 cup rinsed Water
4.5-5 cup Water
2 cup Jaggery
4+4 tbsp Ghee
1/2 coconut pieces
1/4 cup Cashews
2 tbsp Raisins
1/2 tsp Cardamom
pinch of Salt

snippet.title: SYAAPA : EP 01 | COLLEGE RUSTICATE | KANGRA BOYS
snippet.description:
"SYAAPA" is Himachal's first ever web series produced by KANGRA BOYS

"SYAAPA" is the story of four friends and one of their senior advocate Makkhan. In this episode all four friends after being expelled from their college return to their ancestral house in their village. Here they encounter a dead body in their house and all of them are haunted by the fear that they might be accused of his murder. Now, they call one of their college senior advocate Makhan for help. Let's see how these four friends deal with this problem and if advocate Makkhan comes to help them.      

Cast: Rajat Dogra, Sachin Dogra, Puneet Suman, Avraaj Kumar, Arvind Kumar,Gulzar Thukral, Swati Sharma, Shikha Sadwal, Prateeksha Thakur, Akhil Chaudhary , H.S. Gautam, Kartar Rana ,James, Aditya Dhiman , Shivam ,Vishal Deep, Sanjay Chauhan, Rahul, Master Aakhyat Kumar , Master Aditya Sharma,  etc.   

Writer & Director : Arvind Kumar
Produced by: Kangra Boys
DOP :- Praveen Jaggi  
Drone :- Sachin Kumar & Anshul Dixit
DI Colorist  : Akhil Chaudhary 
Music By  : Ketan tomar
Singer : Ankit Shandilya, Poonam Pandit, Krishana & Bindas Bidu 
Lyrics - Ishan Bhatia, Krishna & Bindas Bidu

Tere Bin Episode 07 Teaser - 12th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.description:
Janardhan Wishvanbhar Rane, a widower, has spent his life bringing up his two kids Chirag and Gaurav. Now when the two have grown up, Gaurav takes up his father's responsibility. They manage the household chores and their business as well. One day Gaurav meets his college friend Sheekha Kapoor, who lives with her guardian Anuradha who was Janardan's first love. Gaurav and Sheekha come to know about their past relationship. Now Gaurav wants his father to marry Anuradha.

Movie - Mere Baap Pehle Aap
Starcast - Akshaye Khanna, Paresh Rawal, Genelia D'Souza, Rajpal Yadav, Archana Puran Singh

Janardhan Wishvanbhar Rane, a widower, has spent his life bringing up his two kids Chirag and Gaurav. Now when the two have grown up, Gaurav takes up his father's responsibility. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. snippet.title: AHIMSA Official Trailer | Teja | RP Patnaik | Kiran | Abhiram | Geethika | Rajat Bedi | Sada
snippet.description:
Watch & Enjoy : -- AHIMSA Official Trailer | Teja | RP Patnaik | Kiran | Abhiram | Geethika | Rajat Bedi | Sada

#AHIMSA  #AHIMSATrailer  #Teja #RPPatnaik #Kiran #Geethika #RajatBedi #Sada  

Director Teja, Anandi Arts Creations‚Äô AHIMSA Shoot Wrapped Up

Director Teja has the calibre to deliver blockbusters with stars as well as upcoming actors. He indeed introduced many actors with his films and some of them become stars. He has proved numerous times that content is the king and films with good content do wonders at box office.

Teja is now introducing another debutant Abhiram as a hero with a youthful entertainer Ahimsa. This is going to be perfect Teja mark movie with the story incorporated with all the commercial ingredients.

P Kiran is producing the movie under Anandi Art Creations. Geethika has played Abhiram‚Äôs love interest, wherein Sada and Kamal Kamaraju will be seen in vital roles.

The film‚Äôs pre-look generated lots of curiosity on the film. It also gave an impression that Ahimsa will be high on action. Since the film‚Äôs shoot is wrapped up, the team will be kick-starting the promotional activities.

RP Patnaik who provided numerous chartbuster albums has scored music for the film. Teja, Anandi Arts Creations, and RP Patnaik have joined forces again after Nuvvu Nenu to deliver another musical blockbuster.

The movie has cinematography handled by Sameer Reddy, while Kotagiri Venkateswara Rao is the editor. Anil Achugatla has penned dialogues and Supriya is the art director.

The makers will soon announce the release date of the movie.

Cast: Abhiram, Geethika, Rajat Bedi, Sadha, Ravi Kale, Kamal Kamaraju, Manoj Tiger, Kalpalatha, Devi Prasad and others.

Technical Crew:

Story, Screenplay, Direction : Teja
Producer : P Kiran
Banner : Anandi Art Creations
Music Director : RP Patnaik
DOP : Sameer Reddy
Editor : Kotagiri Venkateswara Rao
Dialogues : Anil Achugatla
Lyrics : Chandrabose

Teja is now introducing another debutant Abhiram as a hero with a youthful entertainer Ahimsa. This is going to be perfect Teja mark movie with the story incorporated with all the commercial ingredients.

P Kiran is producing the movie under Anandi Art Creations. Geethika has played Abhiram‚Äôs love interest, wherein Sada and Kamal Kamaraju will be seen in vital roles.

The film‚Äôs pre-look generated lots of curiosity on the film. It also gave an impression that Ahimsa will be high on action. Since the film‚Äôs shoot is wrapped up, the team will be kick-starting the promotional activities.

RP Patnaik who provided numerous chartbuster albums has scored music for the film. Teja, Anandi Arts Creations, and RP Patnaik have joined forces again after Nuvvu Nenu to deliver another musical blockbuster.

The movie has cinematography handled by Sameer Reddy, while Kotagiri Venkateswara Rao is the editor. Anil Achugatla has penned dialogues and Supriya is the art director.

snippet.title: Shaakuntalam Official Trailer - Telugu | Samantha, Dev Mohan | Gunasekhar | Feb 17, 2023 Release
snippet.description:
Shaakuntalam Official Trailer - Telugu | Samantha, Dev Mohan | Gunasekhar | Feb 17, 2023 Release

Shaakuntalam Movie also in 3D, Written & Directed by Gunasekhar, Presented by Dil Raju under Sri Venkateswara Creations in collaboration with Gunaa Teamworks, Produced by Neelima Guna.

The massively mounted film Shaakuntalam based on internationally acclaimed Kalidasa‚Äôs Sanskrit play ‚ÄòAbhijnana Shakuntalam‚Äô is all set to release in Hindi, Telugu, Tamil, Malayalam & Kannada.  The story of Shaakuntalam revolves around the epic love story of Shakuntala and King Dushyant from Mahabharata, portrayed by Samantha and Dev Mohan.

The film is helmed by supremely proficient, Director Gunasekhar and marks a whimsical tale of love set in the Kashyapa Kanumalu (Kashmir), the grandeur and splendour of Dushyant‚Äôs Puru Dynasty making the film extremely exceptional.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3666 - 12 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3666: Party Sharty Ka Nateeja
--------------------------------------------------------
Even though Bagha is taken to society by all the Gokuldham men, his peculiar conduct persists because of his intoxication. Bagha declines to take the medications when Dr. Hathi brings them out of his office. In an effort to get Bagha to agree to take the medication, Bhide amuses him by making amusing impersonations. Bagha warns everyone that if he is made to take the pills, he will depart in Sodhi's jeep. Bagha refuses to take the tablets. Alarmed, the women of Gokuldham descend to look about. Bagha ascends the balcony and moves closer to the edge. Everyone is concerned that he might lose his balance. Stay tuned!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3666, 12 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000204229

snippet.description:
#DalKhichdi #MakarSankrantiRecipe #pressurecooker #khichdi  #unique #healthy 

INGREDINETS TO MAKE THE RECIPE:
1 Cup Dhuli Moong Dal 
1 Cup Short Grain Rice (i have use sona masoori)
VEGGIES :
1/2 Gobhi 
1/2 Cup Peas
1 Carrot 
7 - 8 Beans 
1 Big Potatoes 
Desi Ghee 
1 tsp Cumin Seeds 
2 Tbsp Salt 
1/2 tsp Haldi Powder 
6 Cups 

INGREDIENTS TO MAKE MASALA

2 Tbsp Coriander Powder 
1 Tbsp Jeera 
1 tsp Salt 
1/2 tsp Ajwain 
1 tsp Black Peppercorns 
2 Tbsp Anardana 
1 Tbsp Amchur Powder 
1 Tbsp Kala Namak 
1 Tbsp Garam Masala 
1 Tbsp Kasuri methi 
1 Tbsp Spicy Red Chilli Powder 

INGREDIENTS FOR TADKA 
1 Tbsp Desi Ghee 
1 Pinch Hing 
3 - 4 Chopped Garlic 
1 tsp Mustard Seeds 
1 tsp Cumin Seeds 
 5 -6  Curry Patta 
2 Dried Chillies

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3667 - 13 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3667: Bagha Ki Zidd
--------------------------------------------------------
Bagha refuses to step off the balcony, and the people of Gokuldham are concerned about him. Nattu Kaka tells Bagha that his actions are unjustified because they are causing unnecessary pain to the innocent Gokuldham dwellers. Jetha speaks about the delivery of his order to Bagha, which ends up disturbing him more. Babita tells Jetha not to discuss the job in this delicate situation. Jetha explains to Babita that he deliberately talked about work because Bagha is very professional and this could distract her spirit from Bawri. Will it really change Bagha's mindset?  Stay tuned!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3667, 13 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

As fate would have it, Bihaan bumps into Thapki once again at the school basketball court. On the persistence of Tina, Bihaan introduces himself to Thapki. But he is taken aback on knowing her name and walks away. Will he recall anything?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. snippet.title: Kya Sahi, Kya Nahi - Maruti Jimny 4x4 India | First Look
snippet.description: Maruti Suzuki Jimny 5-door has finally come to India, as its bookings open today. Upon its launch, it will rival Mahindra Thar thanks to its 4x4 system and body-on-frame architecture. It gets 1.5L K15B engine, which will be offered with a 5-speed manual and 4-speed automatic. Though the prices haven‚Äôt been revealed yet, we expect it to come at Rs 12 lakh.

About Film Companion South:
Film Companion South is a division of Film Companion, founded by film critic and author Anupama Chopra. Apart from film reviews and articles, Film Companion South, with programs in Tamil, Malayalam, Telugu, and Kannada, specializes in conducting in-depth interviews with film personalities which include the likes of Kamal Hassan, Mani Ratnam, Academy Award-winner AR Rahman, Vetrimaaran, Dhanush, Yash, Sruthi Hariharan, Mahesh Babu, NTR Jr, Samantha, Aishwarya Rajesh, Ramya Krishnan, Prithviraj, Anjali Menon, Mysskin, Gautam Vasudev Menon, Rajamouli, Ram Charan, Yash, Prashanth Neel, Venkat Prabhu, Nelson, Sivakarthikeyan, Rakshit Shetty and many more. The channel has also hosted shows which open up the lesser-known facets of filmmaking with conversations with PC Sreeram, Ravi Varman, Rajiv Menon, Thota Tharani, and Academy Award-winner Resul Pookutty. In other words, Film Companion South is for those who love their cinema and are unapologetic about it.

*About* 
------------

Judwa behene Divya aur Drishti ko apne janam se mila hai shakti ka vardaan. Drishti bhavishya kaal ko dekh sakti hai aur Divya ussey badal sakti hai. Inke mata pita ne apni jaan ka balidaan dekar bachaya dono beheno ko par bichad gaye bachpan mai Divya aur Drishti. Alag alag parivaaron mai pale bade par ek doosre ko dhundhte rahe. 
Ek kaali shakti - Pishaachini haasil karna chahti hai sarva shaktishali Kaal Vijay Ratna ko aur saalon se padi hai dono beheno ke peeche. Dobara mil hi jaati hai Divya aur Drishti. Ek saath milkar karti hai muqaabla Pishaachini ka aur karte hai waada ussey khatam karne ka.
